      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.17 - Abu Al-Hasan Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) was asked about the collected water in a public bath from people’s washings, which may get onto clothes.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it”."
        ]
